# Templ — composition & ui8px

## Stack

- **Primitives:** `github.com/fastygo/templ/ui` — `@ui.Stack`, `@ui.Button`, `@ui.Form`, …
- **Composites:** `import cmp "github.com/fastygo/templ/components"`
- **Helpers:** `github.com/fastygo/templ/utils` — `Cn`, `Compose`, ARIA, `tags.go`
- **Preview:** `examples/` — composes facades for local server only

Import shape: `import "github.com/fastygo/templ/ui"` — do **not** deep-import in examples unless testing one package.

## Styling model

| Kind | Mechanism | Where defined |
|------|-----------|---------------|
| `Variant`, `Size`, … | CVA | `*.variants.json` (target) or `*Variants` in `.templ` |
| Layout, spacing, responsive | raw Tailwind | `Class` prop only |
| Design tokens | CSS variables | consumer app or `examples/web/static/css/tokens.css` |

**Forbidden:** semantic layout props (`gap=`, `flex=`, `items=` as component API).  
**Prefer:** `Variant` / `Size` presets over long manual `Class` chains. There is no `unstyled` escape hatch — add a new named variant to the `*.variants.json` when needed.

## Tailwind / ui8px

- Utilities in `Class` strings must pass **[`.ui8px/policy`](../../.ui8px/policy/)**.
- Lint **`ui/`**, **`components/`**, **`utils/`**, and **`examples/`** after class-bearing edits.
- Registry bricks do **not** ship canonical theme CSS — demos use `examples/web/static/css/tokens.css`.
- Allowed preview CSS: `examples/web/static/css/input.css`, `tokens.css`, built `app.css`.

```bash
bun run lint:ui8px
```

## No raw markup in bricks

- **Forbidden:** ad-hoc layout/content tags in **`ui/**`** and **`components/**`** when a primitive or composite exists.
- **Mandatory:** compose `@ui.*` and `@cmp.*`; keep brick files thin (props → classes → one root element).
- **Exception:** brick root element required by semantics (`<dialog>`, `<button>`, landmark tags via `Tag` on `Block`).
- **Examples:** `examples/page.templ` may use document shell tags (`<!DOCTYPE>`, `<html>`, `<head>`, `<body>`, asset tags).

## Variants file

Migrate inline `var XVariants = uiutils.Variants{...}` to colocated `*.variants.json` per [`.project/dual-stack-component-library.md`](../../.project/dual-stack-component-library.md).

Validator must keep `api.enum` ↔ JSON keys in sync.

## Dependencies

- Brick markup: **this module only** — no consumer app imports inside `ui/` or `components/`.
- Default bricks: **no** npm/React deps; no required client bundle.
- Opt-in behavior: `Behavior`, `DataUI8Kit` — see **`templ-aria.mdc`**.

See **`templ-registry-structure.mdc`**, **`templ-validation-testing.mdc`**, **`templ-component-spec.mdc`**.
